    <item>
      <title>随着中国报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/us-stock-futures-swing-as-tariffs-kick-in-china-levies-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票期货在周三延长，S＆amp; p 500指数在熊市的边缘上进行了交易，因为中国对美国进行了报复，并进一步提高了对美国商品的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/us-stock-futures-swing-as-tariffs-kick-in-china-levies-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 07:37:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库抛售在全球范围内发出长期收益率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[较长日期的美国国债的出埃及记出了收益率的飙升，这加剧了自2020年以来最大的抛售，这本来应该是世界上最安全的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/treasuries-fire-sale-sends-long-term-yields-soaring-worldwide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 05:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元高达六个月高的日元高关税驱动避风港需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/yen-rallies-1-as-trump-s-tariffs-drive-haven-demand-m99fi8jf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元在中国对美国关税进行报复后对避风港资产的越来越多的需求激增，促使交易者在日本银行下一次加息时重新考虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/yen-rallies-1-as-trump-s-tariffs-drive-haven-demand-m99fi8jf</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 04:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易动荡跌入美元，国债，黄金飙升了3％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/gold-xauusd-steady-as-traders-brace-for-tariff-hit-to-ramp-up-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）征收新的进口关税和中国以其自己的税款打击之后，黄金集会了多达3％的全球市场，美元逐渐减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/gold-xauusd-steady-as-traders-brace-for-tariff-hit-to-ramp-up-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 01:16:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500设置为靠近熊市，因为债券下沉：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票和债券的踩踏事件在周三收集了势头，因为中国对美国的关税进行了报复，这表明贸易战没有结束，这将S＆amp; p 500推向了熊市的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
